WEBVTT

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:31.456
how do they give patients like Robin
back the sort of control that they need?

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:32.776
And how do they do it

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:36.856
in a way that mainstream
medical hospitals and clinics,

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:39.216
at least for Robin, weren't able to?

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.056
What's their secret?

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:43.736
So I decided to find out.

00:06:43.760 --> 00:06:47.896
I went to a seedy clinic
in Venice Beach in California

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.216
and got a recommendation

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:52.776
that would allow me
to be a medical marijuana patient.

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:56.816
I got a letter of recommendation
that would let me buy medical marijuana.

00:06:56.840 --> 00:06:58.656
I got that recommendation illegally,

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:00.736
because I'm not
a resident of California --